         <div xml:id="kzz7yh-k84307"><!-- l4d21cl -->
            <head xml:id="kzz7yh-k84307-Hd1e101">Circa litteram</head>
            <p xml:id="kzz7yh-k84307-d1e103">
               <lb ed="#V" n="124"/>CIrca litteram. <quote xml:id="kzz7yh-k84307-Qd1e107" source="http://scta.info/resource/pl-l4d21c2-d1e112@37-39">Ad diem 
      damnatio<lb ed="#V" n="125" break="no"/>nis</quote>: supple quantum 
     <lb ed="#V" n="126"/>ad malos. <quote xml:id="kzz7yh-k84307-Qd1e114" source="http://scta.info/resource/pl-l4d21c2-d1e112@40-41">Et remunerationis</quote>: supple quantum ad 
     <lb ed="#V" n="127"/>bonos. <quote xml:id="kzz7yh-k84307-Qd1e120" source="http://scta.info/resource/pl-l4d21c2-d1e112@73-78">Non redarguo: quia forsitan verum est</quote>: non 
      po<lb ed="#V" n="128" break="no"/>nitur ibi forsitan: vt si non dubonis de existentia purgatorii: sed 
      <lb ed="#V" n="129"/>vtrum de illo igne intelligatur illud verbum apostoli primo Cor. 5. quod dicit de 
      <lb ed="#V" n="130"/>illis qui edificant lignum: fenum et stipulam. Nisi aliqua sint 
      frequen<lb ed="#V" n="131" break="no"/>ter nerata: hoc non dicitur: quia venialia frequenter iterata confiteri in 
      <lb ed="#V" n="132"/>speciali sit necessarium. Sed quia est magis securum. Omnibus diebus vite sue 
      <lb ed="#V" n="133"/>ignominiosus pegrinando pergat: quamuis hoc poenitentia reuelatoribus 
      <lb ed="#V" n="134"/>confessionum antiquitus cum depositione iniungeretur: modo tamen 
      loco<lb ed="#V" n="135" break="no"/>pregrinationis illius in arctum monasterium ad agendam poenitentiam 
      <lb ed="#V" n="136"/>detruduntur. <ref xml:id="kzz7yh-k84307-Rd1e142">extra de pe. et re. Omnis vtriusque sexus</ref>
            </p>
